f:["$","p","Depending on the unit condition, the work can include pressure inspection, visible leakage diagnosis, refilling support where required, cooling output test, followed by testing to confirm the AC is performing better before the visit is closed. This matters around Vadodara Junction side and business belt because homes and offices here often run AC units for long hours during warm weather.",{"children":"Depending on the unit condition, the work can include pressure inspection, visible leakage diagnosis, refilling support where required, cooling output test, followed by testing to confirm the AC is performing better before the visit is closed. This matters around Vadodara Junction side and business belt because homes and offices here often run AC units for long hours during warm weather."}]
10:["$","p","Timely AC gas filling can restore faster cooling, prevent extra compressor stress, improve comfort during harsh weather, and help identify leakage before repeat failure. It also helps address complaints like insufficient cooling, ice formation on coils, longer cooling cycles, warm air despite compressor activity before they turn into bigger issues.",{"children":"Timely AC gas filling can restore faster cooling, prevent extra compressor stress, improve comfort during harsh weather, and help identify leakage before repeat failure. It also helps address complaints like insufficient cooling, ice formation on coils, longer cooling cycles, warm air despite compressor activity before they turn into bigger issues."}]
